<?xml version="1.0"?><HotelElement><Id>11894261</Id><Name>Baja Hotels Villas</Name><Region><Id>20904</Id><Name>Cagliari</Name><CityId>17064</CityId></Region><Type>Hotel</Type><Address><Address1>LOC. SANTA GIUSTA</Address1><Address2 /><Address3 /><City>CASTIADAS</City><State /><Zip>09040</Zip><Country>ITALY</Country><Tel>00390709919028</Tel><Fax>0039070991027</Fax><Email>FIT@OVEST.COM</Email><Url /></Address><Stars>4</Stars><GeneralInfo><Latitude>39.61586172</Latitude><Longitude>9.10828816</Longitude></GeneralInfo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>The hotel is set in the midst of a forest and directly in front of the breathtakingly clear ocean. It is easily reached by following a marvellous panoramic road, less than 60 km from Cagliari. Guests will find restaurants, bars and clubs around 1 km away in Costa Rey. The nearest bus and railway stations are in Cagliari, around 70 km away. Shopping is available in Villasimius, some 15 km from the property. Guests may also be interested in visiting Muravera, which is around 20 minutes' drive away.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>The rooms offer an en suite bathroom with a shower and hairdryer, a double bed, direct dial telephone, satellite/cable TV, Internet access, a safe and minibar. Air conditioning and heating are provided and each room features a balcony or terrace.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>This beach hotel, which was built in 2009, offers typical Mediterranean architecture and is warm and sunny. It is also ideal for conferences and work meetings due to its conference room. Other facilities include a lobby, 24-hour reception and check-out service, a hotel safe, lift access to the rooms, newspaper stand and hairdressing salon. Guests can make use of the TV lounge and younger guests can let off steam in the children's playground and kids' club. The hotel features a bar and restaurant. Wireless Internet access is available, and room service and laundry service are offered. A car park and bicycle hire are also provided.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Whirlpool</Code><Text>Whirlpool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HandicapAccessible</Code><Text>Handicap accessible</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>TVInRoom</Code><Text>TV in room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>OutdoorPool</Code><Text>Outdoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Hairdresser</Code><Text>Hairdresser</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>PublicInternetAccess</Code><Text>Public internet access</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>LaundryService</Code><Text>Laundry service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ReceptionArea</Code><Text>Reception Area</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CheckIn24hr</Code><Text>24hr. CheckIn</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Reception24hr</Code><Text>24hr. Reception</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Lift</Code><Text>Lift</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ConferenceRoom</Code><Text>Conference Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>TVRoom</Code><Text>TV Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>DiningRoom</Code><Text>Dining Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RestaurantAirconditioned</Code><Text>Restaurant Air-Conditioned</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RestaurantNonSmokingArea</Code><Text>Restaurant - non-smoking area</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RestaurantSmokingArea</Code><Text>Restaurant Smoking Area</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>WLANAccessPoint</Code><Text>WLAN Access Point</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MedicalService</Code><Text>Medical Service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>BicycleStorage</Code><Text>Bicycle S